import pandas as pd
import os

# Define the path to the Downloads folder (update if needed)
downloads_path = os.path.expanduser("~/Downloads")

# Define file paths
file_path = os.path.join(downloads_path, "birds_merged_dataset.csv")
cleaned_file_path = os.path.join(downloads_path, "birds_merged_dataset_cleaned.csv")

# Load the dataset
df = pd.read_csv(file_path)

# Drop unnecessary columns
df = df.drop(columns=['State_y', 'State'], errors='ignore')

# Rename 'State_x' to 'State'
df = df.rename(columns={'State_x': 'State'})

# Save the cleaned dataset
df.to_csv(cleaned_file_path, index=False)

print(f"Dataset cleaned and saved successfully as '{cleaned_file_path}'.")
